{"tid":1910702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【訪談】被控暴動的樂觀男孩","createTime":"2020-03-05T00:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T13:24:04.000Z","uid":287557,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a49d1cbeaf35b121e57b51ac3bae1d335879bc67","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"「如果我罪成入獄，刑滿後我仍然在香港。在我這個家。」<br />\n<br />\n預計無法畢業，帶著這條控罪，很多事情都要暫停。<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪，刑期以年計。他是前線，被捕了，早有心準備，反而很平靜。<br />\n<br />\n網民不斷比較，誰比誰黃，誰比誰前。於是有人說，運動靜了。<br />\n<br />\n他卻覺得，沒有誰比誰高尚。<br />\n<br />\n「每個人環境不同。有人可以走到最前，有人為養家做和理非。但要走下去，我們都需要對方。」<br />\n<br />\n對話中，他重複最多的一句是，香港人真係好叻。<br />\n<br />\n佔路，接受了。<br />\n火攻，接受了。<br />\n汽油彈，接受了。<br />\n<br />\n一切源自 2014，還有槍聲打響的魚蛋黑夜。<br />\n<br />\n不是偶爾，是前人累積，才有了今天。<br />\n<br />\n「我只是這些人之中，其中一個。」<br />\n<br />\n被捕後，他收到很多慰問。<br />\n<br />\n辛苦了。<br />\n是香港虧欠了你。<br />\n<br />\n這些話語，窩心，但不代表他。<br />\n<br />\n「我沒那麼偉大，不是為香港走上街頭。我純粹想做點什麼，結果做了前線，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n如像香港人接受了抗爭，若是無可避免，那麼，暴動罪也是他的命運。<br />\n<br />\n重新選擇一萬次，還是會上前線。他笑說，改不了，也不後悔。<br />\n<br />\n結果未明，在這刻，他想向大家寄語。<br />\n<br />\n「想走下去的話，記住：不分和勇。」<br />\n<br />\n需要人鏈，需要口號，需要文宣。不可能人人都上前，那麼，珍惜在槍林彈雨中，仍有人在後面。<br />\n<br />\n隨時入獄，前途難料，他總是出奇樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n「最近，如果你覺得靜，不如想盡辦法做文宣。幫忙寫，幫忙分享，一樣是貢獻。」<br />\n<br />\n在這種時期，時間多了，如果你覺得靜，或許是你做得少了。<br />\n<br />\n每人做多一點，也是民意，也是連繫。<br />\n<br />\n帶著這條重罪，這男孩卻很正面。<br />\n<br />\n在宵禁期間，不能晚歸，所以和朋友聚會的次數寥寥可數。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，就珍惜回家吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n「被捕後，最開心是見到爸媽由藍轉黃。看新聞，我還在扒飯，他們已經鬧緊警察。被理解，還是窩心的。」<br />\n<br />\n朋友難見，家人就更重要。以往撐政府，到如今深黃，除了因為兒子，也因為大家。<br />\n<br />\n面對槍火，退縮有何難。但這八個月，我們仍然在這裡。<br />\n<br />\n兩老終於明白了，原來愛這個地方，並非口講，身體會自然行動。<br />\n<br />\n所以，兒子上街了。或會入獄，但不會後悔。<br />\n<br />\n他只願這有限日子，每餐飯，一家人開懷點。<br />\n<br />\n如像他的父母，有人由和理非進化到前線，也有人從港豬進化成和理非。<br />\n<br />\n「步伐不一樣而已。大家是同路人，例如我，被告暴動，也沒那麼高尚。各有各做就好。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇捉鬼？<br />\n「慢慢會調節。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇靜咗？<br />\n「做多啲咪唔靜。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇內鬧？<br />\n「鬥少啲囉。」<br />\n<br />\n我們的對話，沒那麼悲催。<br />\n<br />\n他是正常人，不會因罪名變得不正常。他覺得，自己和所有人一樣，是手足。<br />\n<br />\n不需要被記住，不需要太傷感，只需要繼續行。<br />\n<br />\n不放棄，就是對手足最好的回報。"},{"pid":"999ab80eb04867294b912d710e2c0204a6847b42","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:13:50.000Z","msg":"「我沒有後悔，一秒都未試過。被捕嘛，也沒辦法。抗爭總會有問題，樂觀一點吧，香港人已經好叻。」<br />\n<br />\n平靜，卻還是很感性。運動之中，有驚恐，都有感動。<br />\n<br />\n前線每一次升級，都換來多一點包容。香港人尺度不同了，是在生死逃命，最大的慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n你不割，已經很足夠。<br />\n<br />\n總有灰心時，前線們的行動，常被當作鬼，還有警察的劇本。<br />\n<br />\n日子久了，反駁的聲音也多了。他選擇只開一邊耳朵，聽聽理解的說話。<br />\n<br />\n討論區上隨意的留言，可以傷人，也可以救人。無名的你，或者都救過無名的他。<br />\n<br />\n男孩是這麼樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n書讀不完，或者再讀過。<br />\n宵禁令下，多見家人吧。<br />\n若然罪成，也沒法子吧。<br />\n<br />\n壞事已經夠多，這世道，保持憤怒，也要找一點美好。<br />\n<br />\n例如，他或會失去的幾年，還未到，就嘗嘗家中的老火湯。<br />\n<br />\n做了暴徒，就張開眼，看看現在的香港。<br />\n<br />\n他說，清醒過後，回不去了。<br />\n<br />\n如果做豬比較快樂，那麼，做現在的他，就很好。<br />\n<br />\n這孩子實在樂觀得，叫人笑著笑著，就哭了。<br />\n<br />\n願他平安，走過這一關。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，不要放棄！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"20f59a6247421497055680a531dc12e0c803e518","tid":1910702,"uid":176545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:14:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"034f3fecd990075f62ce08cd0d286e5932ce3106","tid":1910702,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53550d910cfc2101c75c58746b31c5f6ca50fad1","tid":1910702,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fc2e8c9ba645b2ebd50ba7236cbf6a2a6dcbc5","tid":1910702,"uid":23085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"專敬你手足<br />\n亦感謝每一個有付出嘅香港人<br />\n手足講得啱 唔好理人地付出幾多 因為你永遠唔知人地背後做咗幾多野<br />\n最緊要做好自己"},{"pid":"e27fdd9ed166054198f623efdf54c49d4f076166","tid":1910702,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝手足"},{"pid":"e80016ae418f6aa73c5eba70356814a90705cb4c","tid":1910702,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18a58fe92286dbf21c6be8b825a561d61375a13","tid":1910702,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd5604c784c85e1768d5783bd790dc5e3faf5e0","tid":1910702,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23d00a8fe58daacebc9f9a2c5ba345ade5ebda9","tid":1910702,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:56:53.000Z","msg":"多謝手足！"},{"pid":"883c608294ed941ef9499032b4a222b4ede53989","tid":1910702,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76aca529dc9bcbf17bde2c1c16816327e918db0","tid":1910702,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:57:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"23e3de493ba7549bcd653f1bcd7d3b0d64e217df","tid":1910702,"uid":69294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:58:02.000Z","msg":"手足 我地同你出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa3412cfc84e992e0f3b093fec7d52774fbab76","tid":1910702,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd203067d38165e0e28f909e1df81898de9390f6","tid":1910702,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a33d85a072bee2fcf1db2d70c09c1c15150fe99c","tid":1910702,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"尊敬每一個為自由，更好嘅香港而付出的所有人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1721fb7de62be802e7093530261b7a1183f4ce67","tid":1910702,"uid":104592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:04:18.000Z","msg":"人黃都係手足，大家都付出咗血汗時間為香港嘅下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分化、不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb91c386dbbace6511b0135d6099c5778bfaf82","tid":1910702,"uid":329288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:04:20.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b842483a3f7964e84e49670103ba00891fe14701","tid":1910702,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76325f2fbb80e345dced2e5c7f8e59feac105d7","tid":1910702,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dc6c597c4926c99bc96ce9d9772d2bebbaf3cf4","tid":1910702,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"999ab80eb04867294b912d710e2c0204a6847b42","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:13:50.000Z","msg":"「我沒有後悔，一秒都未試過。被捕嘛，也沒辦法。抗爭總會有問題，樂觀一點吧，香港人已經好叻。」<br />\n<br />\n平靜，卻還是很感性。運動之中，有驚恐，都有感動。<br />\n<br />\n前線每一次升級，都換來多一點包容。香港人尺度不同了，是在生死逃命，最大的慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n你不割，已經很足夠。<br />\n<br />\n總有灰心時，前線們的行動，常被當作鬼，還有警察的劇本。<br />\n<br />\n日子久了，反駁的聲音也多了。他選擇只開一邊耳朵，聽聽理解的說話。<br />\n<br />\n討論區上隨意的留言，可以傷人，也可以救人。無名的你，或者都救過無名的他。<br />\n<br />\n男孩是這麼樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n書讀不完，或者再讀過。<br />\n宵禁令下，多見家人吧。<br />\n若然罪成，也沒法子吧。<br />\n<br />\n壞事已經夠多，這世道，保持憤怒，也要找一點美好。<br />\n<br />\n例如，他或會失去的幾年，還未到，就嘗嘗家中的老火湯。<br />\n<br />\n做了暴徒，就張開眼，看看現在的香港。<br />\n<br />\n他說，清醒過後，回不去了。<br />\n<br />\n如果做豬比較快樂，那麼，做現在的他，就很好。<br />\n<br />\n這孩子實在樂觀得，叫人笑著笑著，就哭了。<br />\n<br />\n願他平安，走過這一關。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，不要放棄！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:15:28.000Z","msg":"手足<br />\n真係香港欠左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5f767991b0f701cb4aa71d3b766a518bf0228c","tid":1910702,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7c5df807a3d5a3c30132245eb321cf9066bea8","tid":1910702,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"認同醒過嘅人訓唔返 <br />\n自己不斷係hkg lihkg吸收<br />\n就會想share埋俾更多人聽發生咩事<br />\n知得愈多 根本就無可能放得低做返港豬"},{"pid":"915c3b0241d0bfac9f06aa7707feddb8da904f9f","tid":1910702,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:19:53.000Z","msg":"手足 對你唔住"},{"pid":"0874cec0b5ecb9a09f0f5e343f23c6ef57e3111c","tid":1910702,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238be5f7d34f75e1d99c50b2f58d6eb185624e3c","tid":1910702,"uid":91603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"推 respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a7c37deca3cb8900ee0e49d847b4ba0309b90c","tid":1910702,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6af1fa3e11047e288de90e135dfafee8634577","tid":1910702,"uid":12510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a49d1cbeaf35b121e57b51ac3bae1d335879bc67","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"「如果我罪成入獄，刑滿後我仍然在香港。在我這個家。」<br />\n<br />\n預計無法畢業，帶著這條控罪，很多事情都要暫停。<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪，刑期以年計。他是前線，被捕了，早有心準備，反而很平靜。<br />\n<br />\n網民不斷比較，誰比誰黃，誰比誰前。於是有人說，運動靜了。<br />\n<br />\n他卻覺得，沒有誰比誰高尚。<br />\n<br />\n「每個人環境不同。有人可以走到最前，有人為養家做和理非。但要走下去，我們都需要對方。」<br />\n<br />\n對話中，他重複最多的一句是，香港人真係好叻。<br />\n<br />\n佔路，接受了。<br />\n火攻，接受了。<br />\n汽油彈，接受了。<br />\n<br />\n一切源自 2014，還有槍聲打響的魚蛋黑夜。<br />\n<br />\n不是偶爾，是前人累積，才有了今天。<br />\n<br />\n「我只是這些人之中，其中一個。」<br />\n<br />\n被捕後，他收到很多慰問。<br />\n<br />\n辛苦了。<br />\n是香港虧欠了你。<br />\n<br />\n這些話語，窩心，但不代表他。<br />\n<br />\n「我沒那麼偉大，不是為香港走上街頭。我純粹想做點什麼，結果做了前線，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n如像香港人接受了抗爭，若是無可避免，那麼，暴動罪也是他的命運。<br />\n<br />\n重新選擇一萬次，還是會上前線。他笑說，改不了，也不後悔。<br />\n<br />\n結果未明，在這刻，他想向大家寄語。<br />\n<br />\n「想走下去的話，記住：不分和勇。」<br />\n<br />\n需要人鏈，需要口號，需要文宣。不可能人人都上前，那麼，珍惜在槍林彈雨中，仍有人在後面。<br />\n<br />\n隨時入獄，前途難料，他總是出奇樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n「最近，如果你覺得靜，不如想盡辦法做文宣。幫忙寫，幫忙分享，一樣是貢獻。」<br />\n<br />\n在這種時期，時間多了，如果你覺得靜，或許是你做得少了。<br />\n<br />\n每人做多一點，也是民意，也是連繫。<br />\n<br />\n帶著這條重罪，這男孩卻很正面。<br />\n<br />\n在宵禁期間，不能晚歸，所以和朋友聚會的次數寥寥可數。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，就珍惜回家吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n「被捕後，最開心是見到爸媽由藍轉黃。看新聞，我還在扒飯，他們已經鬧緊警察。被理解，還是窩心的。」<br />\n<br />\n朋友難見，家人就更重要。以往撐政府，到如今深黃，除了因為兒子，也因為大家。<br />\n<br />\n面對槍火，退縮有何難。但這八個月，我們仍然在這裡。<br />\n<br />\n兩老終於明白了，原來愛這個地方，並非口講，身體會自然行動。<br />\n<br />\n所以，兒子上街了。或會入獄，但不會後悔。<br />\n<br />\n他只願這有限日子，每餐飯，一家人開懷點。<br />\n<br />\n如像他的父母，有人由和理非進化到前線，也有人從港豬進化成和理非。<br />\n<br />\n「步伐不一樣而已。大家是同路人，例如我，被告暴動，也沒那麼高尚。各有各做就好。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇捉鬼？<br />\n「慢慢會調節。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇靜咗？<br />\n「做多啲咪唔靜。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇內鬧？<br />\n「鬥少啲囉。」<br />\n<br />\n我們的對話，沒那麼悲催。<br />\n<br />\n他是正常人，不會因罪名變得不正常。他覺得，自己和所有人一樣，是手足。<br />\n<br />\n不需要被記住，不需要太傷感，只需要繼續行。<br />\n<br />\n不放棄，就是對手足最好的回報。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"樓主下次可以補番 sources<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108102623935984/posts/194733238606255/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108102623935984%2Fposts%2F194733238606255%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=2e3613e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108102623935984/posts/194733238606255/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n頂置我喇"},{"pid":"98d9467feaa7281a4101c88bf5bc8d6fe7a3559f","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc6af1fa3e11047e288de90e135dfafee8634577","tid":1910702,"uid":12510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a49d1cbeaf35b121e57b51ac3bae1d335879bc67","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"「如果我罪成入獄，刑滿後我仍然在香港。在我這個家。」<br />\n<br />\n預計無法畢業，帶著這條控罪，很多事情都要暫停。<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪，刑期以年計。他是前線，被捕了，早有心準備，反而很平靜。<br />\n<br />\n網民不斷比較，誰比誰黃，誰比誰前。於是有人說，運動靜了。<br />\n<br />\n他卻覺得，沒有誰比誰高尚。<br />\n<br />\n「每個人環境不同。有人可以走到最前，有人為養家做和理非。但要走下去，我們都需要對方。」<br />\n<br />\n對話中，他重複最多的一句是，香港人真係好叻。<br />\n<br />\n佔路，接受了。<br />\n火攻，接受了。<br />\n汽油彈，接受了。<br />\n<br />\n一切源自 2014，還有槍聲打響的魚蛋黑夜。<br />\n<br />\n不是偶爾，是前人累積，才有了今天。<br />\n<br />\n「我只是這些人之中，其中一個。」<br />\n<br />\n被捕後，他收到很多慰問。<br />\n<br />\n辛苦了。<br />\n是香港虧欠了你。<br />\n<br />\n這些話語，窩心，但不代表他。<br />\n<br />\n「我沒那麼偉大，不是為香港走上街頭。我純粹想做點什麼，結果做了前線，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n如像香港人接受了抗爭，若是無可避免，那麼，暴動罪也是他的命運。<br />\n<br />\n重新選擇一萬次，還是會上前線。他笑說，改不了，也不後悔。<br />\n<br />\n結果未明，在這刻，他想向大家寄語。<br />\n<br />\n「想走下去的話，記住：不分和勇。」<br />\n<br />\n需要人鏈，需要口號，需要文宣。不可能人人都上前，那麼，珍惜在槍林彈雨中，仍有人在後面。<br />\n<br />\n隨時入獄，前途難料，他總是出奇樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n「最近，如果你覺得靜，不如想盡辦法做文宣。幫忙寫，幫忙分享，一樣是貢獻。」<br />\n<br />\n在這種時期，時間多了，如果你覺得靜，或許是你做得少了。<br />\n<br />\n每人做多一點，也是民意，也是連繫。<br />\n<br />\n帶著這條重罪，這男孩卻很正面。<br />\n<br />\n在宵禁期間，不能晚歸，所以和朋友聚會的次數寥寥可數。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，就珍惜回家吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n「被捕後，最開心是見到爸媽由藍轉黃。看新聞，我還在扒飯，他們已經鬧緊警察。被理解，還是窩心的。」<br />\n<br />\n朋友難見，家人就更重要。以往撐政府，到如今深黃，除了因為兒子，也因為大家。<br />\n<br />\n面對槍火，退縮有何難。但這八個月，我們仍然在這裡。<br />\n<br />\n兩老終於明白了，原來愛這個地方，並非口講，身體會自然行動。<br />\n<br />\n所以，兒子上街了。或會入獄，但不會後悔。<br />\n<br />\n他只願這有限日子，每餐飯，一家人開懷點。<br />\n<br />\n如像他的父母，有人由和理非進化到前線，也有人從港豬進化成和理非。<br />\n<br />\n「步伐不一樣而已。大家是同路人，例如我，被告暴動，也沒那麼高尚。各有各做就好。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇捉鬼？<br />\n「慢慢會調節。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇靜咗？<br />\n「做多啲咪唔靜。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇內鬧？<br />\n「鬥少啲囉。」<br />\n<br />\n我們的對話，沒那麼悲催。<br />\n<br />\n他是正常人，不會因罪名變得不正常。他覺得，自己和所有人一樣，是手足。<br />\n<br />\n不需要被記住，不需要太傷感，只需要繼續行。<br />\n<br />\n不放棄，就是對手足最好的回報。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"樓主下次可以補番 sources<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108102623935984/posts/194733238606255/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108102623935984%2Fposts%2F194733238606255%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=2e3613e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108102623935984/posts/194733238606255/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n頂置我喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"好，少開post😅😅唔好怪我<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A8%AA%E8%AB%87-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%25AB%2587-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25A9%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=01091c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%25AB%2587-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25A9%2F&h=3a93e51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A8%AA%E8%AB%87-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"dbe18a29f89c0eef19950cf6bbab71b9fe704627","tid":1910702,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2ff38d93bb1e5a15c02f42dbdb6fc532633c16","tid":1910702,"uid":38821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:32:01.000Z","msg":"點睇捉鬼？<br />\n「慢慢會調節。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇靜咗？<br />\n「做多啲咪唔靜。」<br />\n<br />\n點睇內鬧？<br />\n「鬥少啲囉。」<br />\n<br />\n真手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d4e2f3622adac0273deba97865b74e351c69dc","tid":1910702,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"預備坐監啦，蠢過豬"},{"pid":"b82fbb829026b19be5d35c4ca234653d59d9402c","tid":1910702,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2d8a21460cdc91ccede6860a748a356f74d3a9","tid":1910702,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2d4e2f3622adac0273deba97865b74e351c69dc","tid":1910702,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"預備坐監啦，蠢過豬"},"cit